The TMNT turn 40 this year making them some pretty old teenagers. Since their comic book debut they have had success in multiple mediums and are considered merchandise juggernauts. What happens when our favorite heroes in a half-shell are confronted by the World's Greatest Detective? You get Batman VS The TMNT a 2019 animated film, crossing over these two incredibly popular IPs! Join us as we discuss the animated film, how it differs from the comic book it is named after, and hear us laugh about all the hijinx our protagonist endure in fun-filled episode of the Major Issues Podcast! Cowabunga! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

 

